CONSEQUENTLY, DISPOSE OF EXISTING SPACE THAT HAD BEEN HELD FOR

POTENTIAL GROWTH. THESE EXIT COSTS MAY BE MATERIAL TO OUR

RESULTS OF OPERATIONS IN A GIVEN PERIOD.

