SWAP A SUBSTANTIAL PORTION OF OUR LONG-TERM BORROWINGS INTO U.S.

DOLLAR OBLIGATIONS WITH SHORT-TERM FLOATING INTEREST RATES IN

ORDER TO MINIMIZE OUR EXPOSURE TO INTEREST RATES AND FOREIGN

EXCHANGE MOVEMENTS.

FOR A DISCUSSION OF FACTORS THAT COULD IMPAIR OUR ABILITY TO

