FLOATING RATE OBLIGATIONS. ACCORDINGLY, THE CARRYING VALUE OF

UNSECURED LONG-TERM BORROWINGS APPROXIMATED FAIR VALUE AS OF

NOVEMBER 2007 AND NOVEMBER 2006.

