EACH SHARE OF PREFERRED STOCK ISSUED AND OUTSTANDING HAS A PAR

VALUE OF $0.01, HAS A LIQUIDATION PREFERENCE OF $25,000, IS

REPRESENTED BY 1,000 DEPOSITARY SHARES AND IS REDEEMABLE AT THE

